title: Billy Cobham - drumtalk [episode 21]
description:
Jazz Fusion legend Billy Cobham (Mahavishnu Orchestra, Miles Davis) doesn't simply answer a question -- when he talks you will get some serious advice about how you can become a better musician. Still thankful for the opportunity to speak with such a great artist...
